io.elimu.a2d2.cds.fhir.helper

Class FhirFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elimu.a2d2.cds.fhir.helper.FhirFuture<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the return type of the Future

    public class FhirFuture<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Future extension that will be used for async calls to the FHIR server. When the owner of this object will call get() the thread will lock until the response is returned from the FHIR server.
